<#
IMPORTANT:
Deleting directories and files is a dangerous operation.
Do so with great caution and care.

Here are some neccessary commands to memorize:
Remove-Item: rm
Remove-Item -Recurse: rm -Recurse


Why do we need Recurse?
Recurse is used to delete a directory and ALL of its contents.
#>

# Remove a directory : rm -Recurse
Remove-Item 'yellow folder' -Recurse